Dataset Information

Dataset Name - FER2013 (Facial Expression Recognition 2013)

 Dataset Source - Kaggle

Dataset Link - https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/msambare/fer2013

 Dataset Description - The FER2013 dataset contains grayscale facial images of size 48×48 pixels. The images are categorized into seven emotion classes:

* Angry
* Disgust
* Fear
* Happy
* Neutral
* Sad
* Surprise

Dataset Statistics

* Training Images: ~28,709
* Testing Images: ~7,178
* Total Images: ~35,887
* Number of Classes: 7
* Image Type: Grayscale (48×48 pixels)
